{"tid":515531,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新移民學童2018願望：希望未來會有措施鼓勵大眾尊重新移民","createTime":"2017-12-31T14:01:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-31T15:46:14.000Z","uid":5195,"like":3,"dislike":102,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"749f70885a57575c2fb79d99615a4a0929674ad7","tid":515531,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T14:01:31.000Z","msg":"團體發表報告，就政府今年跟進兒童貧窮問題的表現評分，以總分100計算，政府獲評歷年最高的25分，較去年多10分，但整體仍不合格。<br />\n<br />\n有與母親租住僅百呎劏房的兒童說，家中環境狹窄只能擺放一張床，沒有地方做功課，梯間常有老鼠出沒，衞生環境惡劣。他期望，新一年政府能加快增建公屋，早日上樓。<br />\n<br />\n亦有新移民學童說，曾試過與朋友用普通話交談，但招來他人歧視目光，她希望未來會有措施鼓勵大眾尊重新移民。<br />\n<br />\n此份報告由社區組織協會與兒童權利關注會發表，訪問了2000多名兒童。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1372680_1_L_20171231143930.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1372680_1_L_20171231143930.jpg&h=f81dd5f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃雄濤小朋友期望，新一年政府增建公屋，早日上樓。（關可為攝）"},{"pid":"08aa7729c0351730ed08759de6c643e1646a44af","tid":515531,"uid":46527,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T14:02:30.000Z","msg":"無可能"},{"pid":"31c05ec8708727f3b4d4a24019c17d203f60067f","tid":515531,"uid":164928,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T14:02:58.000Z","msg":"快回祖國懷抱 香港很危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f23d7fb5efdb69e3169e9b1c8e34b290545121e7","tid":515531,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T14:03:08.000Z","msg":"戴耀廷點睇"},{"pid":"7114dd2c9ce539e2d5e1a75a1d9d3c6ee7b4dacf","tid":515531,"uid":36551,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T14:03:25.000Z","msg":"屌你老母養到D支那豬咁撚肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dccbd77f7d76893eb6df79ea3649bc330b7356f","tid":515531,"uid":116688,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T14:04:21.000Z","msg":"有冇問過香港人有乜願望呀屌你"},{"pid":"e95874e344f07f83fff8ce21d1ce2921a7be2e1f